              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-800 mb-3 group-hover:text-green-600 transition-colors">
                <a href="/blog/why-windows-steam-up-how-to-fix-bishops-stortford">Why Windows Steam Up</a>
