              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Complete guide to eliminating condensation and steamy windows permanently.</p>
              <a href="/blog/why-windows-steam-up-how-to-fix-bishops-stortford" class="text-green-600 hover:text-green-700 font-semibold flex items-center">
