            <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 pb-5">
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Yes. Our emergency repair service operates 24/7 with rapid response times—usually within 2 hours—to secure your property with temporary fixes such as boarding up and to carry out urgent repairs promptly.</p>
